title: International imports in all services in Canada 2020
summary: This graph shows International imports in all services ( million of dollars ) to Canada during 2020 , each Month .
There is a general upward trend .
The graph was at its lowest in Feb and highest in Dec .
gold: A line chart about international imports in all services in Canada in 2020 . The imports drop slightly from 15000 million dollars to 14000 million dollars from January to March . Then the imports fall dramatically to 10000 million dollars in April , then maintain the same level for the rest of the year .
